column2: all my limbs are jumping on their own accord
two cortisone injections to get my shoulder right
hasn't stopped shaking her leg the entire hour
the only reason I haven't downed all these antidepressants is because sertraline overdose rarely results in death
feel like you aren't a human anymore
knocked me on my ass last night
wide awake yet again past 1:00 a.m
makes you want to do stuff
